{"tha-ap452:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap452:0.2":"Vibhitakavagga ","tha-ap452:0.3":"10 Bodhigharadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap452:1.1":"“Siddhatthassa bhagavato, ","tha-ap452:1.2":"dvipadindassa tadino; ","tha-ap452:1.3":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap452:1.4":"bodhigharamakarayim. ","tha-ap452:2.1":"Tusitam upapannomhi, ","tha-ap452:2.2":"vasami ratane ghare; ","tha-ap452:2.3":"Na me sitam va unham va, ","tha-ap452:2.4":"vato gatte na samphuse. ","tha-ap452:3.1":"Pancasatthimhito kappe, ","tha-ap452:3.2":"cakkavatti ahosaham; ","tha-ap452:3.3":"Kasikam nama nagaram, ","tha-ap452:3.4":"vissakammena mapitam. ","tha-ap452:4.1":"Dasayojanaayamam, ","tha-ap452:4.2":"atthayojanavitthatam; ","tha-ap452:4.3":"Na tamhi nagare atthi, ","tha-ap452:4.4":"kattham valli ca mattika. ","tha-ap452:5.1":"Tiriyam yojanam asi, ","tha-ap452:5.2":"addhayojanavitthatam; ","tha-ap452:5.3":"Mangalo nama pasado, ","tha-ap452:5.4":"vissakammena mapito. ","tha-ap452:6.1":"Cullasitisahassani, ","tha-ap452:6.2":"thambha sonnamaya ahum; ","tha-ap452:6.3":"Manimaya ca niyyuha, ","tha-ap452:6.4":"chadanam rupiyam ahu. ","tha-ap452:7.1":"Sabbasonnamayam gharam, ","tha-ap452:7.2":"vissakammena mapitam; ","tha-ap452:7.3":"Ajjhavuttham maya etam, ","tha-ap452:7.4":"gharadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap452:8.1":"Te sabbe anubhotvana, ","tha-ap452:8.2":"devamanusake bhave; ","tha-ap452:8.3":"Ajjhapattomhi nibbanam, ","tha-ap452:8.4":"santipadamanuttaram. ","tha-ap452:9.1":"Timsakappasahassamhi, ","tha-ap452:9.2":"bodhigharamakarayim; ","tha-ap452:9.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap452:9.4":"gharadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap452:10.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap452:10.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap452:10.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap452:11.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap452:11.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap452:11.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap452:12.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap452:12.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap452:12.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap452:13.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma bodhigharadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap452:14.1":"Bodhigharadayakattherassapadanam dasamam. ","tha-ap452:15.1":"Vibhitakavaggo pancacattalisamo. ","tha-ap452:16.1":"Tassuddanam ","tha-ap452:17.1":"Vibhitaki kolaphali, ","tha-ap452:17.2":"billabhallatakappado; ","tha-ap452:17.3":"Uttalambataki ceva, ","tha-ap452:17.4":"asani padapithako. ","tha-ap452:18.1":"Vediko bodhighariko, ","tha-ap452:18.2":"gathayo ganitapi ca; ","tha-ap452:18.3":"Ekunasitika sabba, ","tha-ap452:18.4":"asmim vagge pakittita. "}